      "participants": "Coordinator + all participant nodes (resource managers).",
      "steps": [
        "Coordinator asks each participant to ‘prepare’ the transaction (usually: to ensure it can commit and to make required locks/records durable).",
        "Each participant responds with either ‘YES’ (prepared/ready to commit) or ‘NO/FAIL’ (cannot safely commit)."
      ],
      "decision_point": "If the coordinator receives YES from all participants, it decides to commit; otherwise it decides to abort."
