        "Coordinator sends a final decision to all participants: ‘COMMIT’ if everyone voted YES, otherwise ‘ABORT’.",
        "On receiving COMMIT, each participant permanently applies the transaction and releases resources/locks; on receiving ABORT, each participant rolls back/reverts and releases resources/locks."
      ],
      "result": "All participants reach the same final outcome (commit or abort), achieving atomicity."
    }
  },
